706080f-a.title: Brooklyn: Nostrand Avenue - Myrtle Avenue
706080f-a.text:
Nostrand Ave., east side, between Myrtle and Vernon Aves. This view is
taken,looking southeast. The house at the left, faces on Vernon Ave. The
orchard is all that remains of the Bsoerum farm.
About 191O.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
